# Redesign Character Pipeline — Based on Full Audit

## Audit Findings (Current Code)

### Bug 1: Visual Bible chỉ chạy có điều kiện
**File**: [process_controller.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/process_controller.py) line 248-295
```
if character_sheet  → character pipeline (ok)
elif historical     → visual bible
else                → KHÔNG CÓ GÌ ← SAI
```
**Đúng**: Visual Bible LUÔN phải chạy.

### Bug 2: Character pipeline kết quả thay thế visual bible
**File**: [process_controller.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/process_controller.py) line 268
```python
visual_bible = pipeline_result  # ← character bible được truyền vào biến visual_bible
```
**Vấn đề**: Character bible KHÔNG PHẢI visual bible. Chúng là **2 thứ khác nhau**.

### Bug 3: [_build_user_message](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/prompt_generator.py#202-279) bảo AI không mô tả ngoại hình cho TẤT CẢ characters
**File**: [prompt_generator.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/prompt_generator.py) line 214-221  
```
"Do NOT describe their physical appearance, clothing, or weapons"
```
**Vấn đề**: Đúng cho PROTAGONIST/NAMED (có --cref), nhưng **SAI cho MILITARY** (cần mô tả quân phục trong prompt).

### Bug 4: [_locations.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/7.Youtube/2.%20Mysteries%20Top%20list/3.%20Merge%20tao%20kich%20ban%20moi/001_Nh%E1%BB%AFng_B%C3%AD_M%E1%BA%ADt_%C4%90en_T%E1%BB%91i_C%E1%BB%A7a_Th%E1%BA%BF_Chi%E1%BA%BFn_II/tts/Test1/_locations.txt) trùng với KEY LOCATIONS trong Visual Bible
Visual Bible đã có section `## KEY LOCATIONS & ARCHITECTURE`. File [_locations.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/7.Youtube/2.%20Mysteries%20Top%20list/3.%20Merge%20tao%20kich%20ban%20moi/001_Nh%E1%BB%AFng_B%C3%AD_M%E1%BA%ADt_%C4%90en_T%E1%BB%91i_C%E1%BB%A7a_Th%E1%BA%BF_Chi%E1%BA%BFn_II/tts/Test1/_locations.txt) riêng là **thừa**.

