## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [process_controller.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/process_controller.py)

1. Visual Bible **LUÔN** chạy (bỏ điều kiện `historical`)
2. Character Pipeline chạy **thêm** khi bật Character Sheet
3. Truyền **cả 2** vào prompt generator: [visual_bible](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#49-64) + [character_bible](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#651-676)
4. Bỏ [_locations.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/7.Youtube/2.%20Mysteries%20Top%20list/3.%20Merge%20tao%20kich%20ban%20moi/001_Nh%E1%BB%AFng_B%C3%AD_M%E1%BA%ADt_%C4%90en_T%E1%BB%91i_C%E1%BB%A7a_Th%E1%BA%BF_Chi%E1%BA%BFn_II/tts/Test1/_locations.txt) riêng (đã có trong Visual Bible)

### [MODIFY] [prompt_generator.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/prompt_generator.py)

1. [_build_user_message()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/prompt_generator.py#202-279) nhận thêm tham số [character_bible](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/narrative_review.py#651-676)
2. Khi có character_bible:
   - PROTAGONIST/NAMED labels → ghi rõ "dùng LABEL, không mô tả ngoại hình"
   - MILITARY descriptions → ghi rõ "mô tả quân phục theo bible"
3. Visual Bible → ghi rõ "dùng cho bối cảnh, dân thường, kiến trúc"

### [MODIFY] [narrative_review_prompt.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/prompts/narrative_review_prompt.txt)

Khi Character Sheet ON: Visual Bible **KHÔNG mô tả nhân vật đã có trong character bible**
→ Chỉ mô tả: civilians, architecture, props, context

### [DELETE] location_prompt.txt — chức năng gộp vào Visual Bible

### Scan + Group prompts — đã sửa xong ở bước trước

